    "APARTMENTS WANTED Cont fHREE MONTHS RENT IN ADVANCE Young couple unfurn apt for 1824 months J5065 rent AT 7867 26 FURNISHED APT 2 or 3 rooms kitchen bath convenient to Munitions Bldg by major and wife just returned from over seas MI 2270 30 DIPLOMAT and family desire 2 or 3 bed rm furn or unfurn apt nw section NA 0411 10 to 4 pm weekdays NAVY LT back after 2 yrs in Pacific seeks 1 bedrm unfurn apt for bride he acquires Easter AL DUNCAN RE Ext 71332 evenings ME 5718 APT furn or unfurn for a yr or less nw section or Chevy Chase 1 or more beorms best references Phone OR 2017 SMALL FURN APT refined naval officer couple no children pets Arlington se Preferred immediate occupancy 85 CH 2000 Ext 183 FURNISHED OR UNFURNISHED apart ment desired by young employed couple in nw or Virginia will sublet or lease excel references Box 122K Star 26 PERMANENT NAVAL OFFICER desires 1 or 2 bedroom apartment within 25 minutes Navy Yard Phone FR 5700 Ext 2506 LT BENNETT 25 APT IN CHICAGOWill exchange for 2 bedroom apt here Navy It separated from family for 19 months CO 1531"
